			<div class="content" id="post-content-4042902">
									

<p>Mr Night Shamalamadingdong. What a twist! Masquerades are everywhere in this game.</p>
<p>presumed typos 'n' stuff -</p>
<ul>
<li>&quot;his superiors had put him up in an silly ghost costume&quot; &#8230; perhaps edited from &quot;an idiotic&quot;?</li>
<li>&quot;a couple&quot; of cookies (implying two), one taken&#8230; twenty minutes later, they've &quot;almost&quot; run out?</li>
<li>one of Night's lines of text is smaller than the others and, at least on my screen, borderline unreadable due to the combination of font and point-size.</li>
<li>sure there was something else but can't remember, or see it on skimming through again</li>
</ul>
<p>&#8230;and one of the quartet seems to talk in an odd fashion lacking natural contractions, but that may just be an affectation.</p>
<p>Also, what is that font and how did you get it to render? I can't see the secret source in the wikicode version, and I don't recognise it as one I have installed.</p>

