<p>I've fixed the a/an error. &quot;Couple&quot; was being used in the more informal capacity of &quot;small number&quot;; I've changed it to few to be clearer. All of Night's dialogue is a little smaller than it'd normally be and is shrunk to 90% &#8212; one line was at 80% and has been brought in line to the rest.</p>
<p>Bones not speaking in contractions is intentional. It's just meant to be a minor quirk to differentiate him.</p>
<p>The font is alpha_echoregular and is imported onto the page by <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;component:chicago-spirit]]</span>, which is the first line in the source code (which imports it onto itself from the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/component:spirit-theme">Chicago Spirit Theme</a>.</p>

